{"tid":1677181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做匙扣俾校長兇話要告佢嗰位手足爸爸，有無嘢要幫忙？","createTime":"2019-10-27T02:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T16:14:08.000Z","uid":288632,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3122a88c2dfce7ce48c6de56c2bf759501d60012","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"琴日見到有個中學生做匙扣俾校長兇話要告佢侵權。見完家長嗰位手足爸爸喺街上嚎哭。唔知你聯絡資料，想話你知:<br />\n<br />\n1. 侵權唔係刑事，唔洗嚎哭。我亦唔信佢會花$告身無分文既學生。<br />\n2. 佢告學生，我免費幫你。<br />\n3. 面對欺人太甚有強權無良心校長必須堅強勇敢有智慧。咪喺街喊教壞細路。"},{"pid":"3da7aa402c58539897f1d8534f33205ce1764696","tid":1677181,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">呢場運動係一個賭注，如果香港人有足夠公民質素， 我哋就會贏\nhttps://lih.kg/1677074\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3c4adca3e88f4fa2fa8d19487b1ab0107caddcf4","tid":1677181,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0d2b7cc1632b95c09663f7b2a0e69eb680bd8e5","tid":1677181,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"有冇details?"},{"pid":"2fc8e399ab79994dfd39993b6b82f8d49178c3c3","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"自推～尋爸1"},{"pid":"62507271bc2e41a04ade5375209920aa11628410","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"3ff1a33304e5a1c71b6d872667f619b4adfceea6","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:01.000Z","msg":"自～推～3"},{"pid":"525489ac3157220c3b08681a6351eb81ae359860","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"自～推4"},{"pid":"258ba18c0709d5c261c22fb240dd830773a9b247","tid":1677181,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20